sentence: in memory of robert eugene hartman -- tillman funeral home & crematory| in memoriam of robert eugene hartman facts.
robert eugene hartman, age 91, of west palm beach, passed away june 12, 2015.
hartman was born in nappanee, indiana on december 2, 1923. he is survived by his sister, sharon chapman of syracuse, indiana.
there will be no local services for mr.
hartman at tillman funeral home & crematory.
all services are under the care of thompson-lengacher-yoder funeral home in nappanee, indiana.
please contact the funeral home at 877-773-3173 for further information.
